   There are dozens of signs for the English concept of "layer."  
			The right sign for "layer" is going to depend on what you mean.
   <br/>
   <br/>
   If you mean "layer" as in a "level" you can use the "flat" sign.
   <br/>
   <br/>
   FLAT / level / floor / carpet / shelf:
